=head1 DESCRIPTION

Resource permission for a dataset. When you create a dataset, all the
other members of the same user group inherit access to the dataset. You
can only create a dataset if your user group has application permission
for Create Datasets.

The following is a list of valid dataset permissions that you can
apply:

=over

=item *

C<ViewDatasetDetails>

=item *

C<ReadDatasetDetails>

=item *

C<AddDatasetData>

=item *

C<CreateDataView>

=item *

C<EditDatasetMetadata>

=item *

C<DeleteDataset>

=back

For more information on the dataset permissions, see Supported Dataset
Permissions
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/finspace/latest/userguide/managing-user-permissions.html#supported-dataset-permissions)
in the FinSpace User Guide.

